{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"VREyeParameters","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/VREyeParameters","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebVR_API\">WebVR API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VREyeParameters\"><code>VREyeParameters</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VREyeParameters/fieldOfView\"><code>fieldOfView</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VREyeParameters/maximumFieldOfView\"><code>maximumFieldOfView</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/VREyeParameters/minimumFieldOfView\"><code>minimumFieldOfView</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VREyeParameters/offset\"><code>offset</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VREyeParameters/renderHeight\"><code>renderHeight</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VREyeParameters/renderWidth\"><code>renderWidth</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>WebVR API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Gamepad/displayId\"><code>Gamepad.displayId</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator/activeVRDisplays\"><code>Navigator.activeVRDisplays</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator/getVRDisplays\"><code>Navigator.getVRDisplays()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay\"><code>VRDisplay</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRDisplayCapabilities\"><code>VRDisplayCapabilities</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRDisplayEvent\"><code>VRDisplayEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRFieldOfView\"><code>VRFieldOfView</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRFrameData\"><code>VRFrameData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRLayerInit\"><code>VRLayerInit</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRPose\"><code>VRPose</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRStageParameters\"><code>VRStageParameters</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>これは<a href=\"/ja/docs/MDN/Writing_guidelines/Experimental_deprecated_obsolete#experimental\">実験的な機能</a>です。</strong><br>本番で使用する前に<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">ブラウザー互換性一覧表</a>をチェックしてください。</p></div>\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebVR_API\">WebVR API</a> の <strong><code>VREyeParameters</code></strong> インターフェイスは，指定した眼のためにシーンを正しくレンダリングするためのすべての情報（視界(field of view)の情報を含む）を表現します．</p>\n<p>このインターフェイスは <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VRDisplay/getEyeParameters\"><code>VRDisplay.getEyeParameters()</code></a> メソッドを通じてアクセスできます．</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"プロパティ","title":"プロパティ","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"vreyeparameters.offset\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VREyeParameters/offset\"><code>VREyeParameters.offset</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><em>ユーザの両眼の中心点から指定した眼の中心へのオフセット量を示します．単位はメートルです．</em></p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"vreyeparameters.fieldofview\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VREyeParameters/fieldOfView\"><code>VREyeParameters.fieldOfView</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><em>指定した眼の現在の視界(FOV)を示しています．これはユーザが瞳孔間距離(IPD)の調整することによって変化します．</em></p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"vreyeparameters.renderwidth\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VREyeParameters/renderWidth\"><code>VREyeParameters.renderWidth</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>それぞれの眼のビューポートの推奨レンダーターゲット幅を示します．単位はピクセルです．</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"vreyeparameters.renderheight\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/VREyeParameters/renderHeight\"><code>VREyeParameters.renderHeight</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>それぞれの眼のビューポートの推奨レンダーターゲット高さを示します．単位はピクセルです．</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">TBD.\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Specification</th>\n      <th>Status</th>\n      <th>Comment</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"about:unknown#vreyeparameters\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\">Unknown<br><small lang=\"ja\">VREyeParameters の定義</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-\">不明</span></td>\n      <td>Initial definition</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザの互換性","id":"ブラウザの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"api.VREyeParameters","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/VREyeParameters/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/WebVR_API\">WebVR API homepage</a>.</li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://mozvr.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MozVr.com</a> — Mozilla VR チームのデモ，ダウンロード，その他のリソース．</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"プロパティ","id":"プロパティ"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様","id":"仕様"},{"text":"ブラウザの互換性","id":"ブラウザの互換性"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"WebVR API の VREyeParameters インターフェイスは，指定した眼のためにシーンを正しくレンダリングするためのすべての情報（視界(field of view)の情報を含む）を表現します．","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"VREyeParameters","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"VREyeParameters","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/vreyeparameters","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/vreyeparameters/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/VREyeParameters","title":"VREyeParameters"}],"pageTitle":"VREyeParameters - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":f